<h4 id="toc0"><span>NOTICE FROM THE CENTRAL INTELLIGENCE COORDINATION</span></h4>
<h4 id="toc1"><span>AND PROJECTS OPERATION COMMAND OFFICE</span></h4>
<p>There is nothing new to report regarding SPC-001 at this time.</p>
